      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Version-controlled solver with documented test suite and regression results covering hemolysis model routines.",
      "rationale": "Solver version control is in place but formal regression test suite does not cover the user-defined hemolysis scalar transport routines. Achieved level 2 against required level 4 at MRL 5."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Method of manufactured solutions or equivalent applied to governing equations including hemolysis transport equation.",
      "rationale": "Code verification was applied to the Navier-Stokes solver only; the hemolysis power-law source term was not subjected to manufactured-solution testing. Gap identified at MRL 5."
    },
    {
