      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative convergence, round-off, and time-integration error quantified and shown negligible relative to hemolysis QoI.",
      "rationale": "Solver error budget not assembled. Residual convergence criteria documented but contribution of iterative error to hemolysis scalar accumulation not evaluated. Flagged as epistemic gap."
