      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Systematic evaluation of turbulence model and hemolysis power-law exponent selection with sensitivity analysis and literature-based justification for Class III VAD flows.",
      "rationale": "k-omega SST turbulence model selected without comparative evaluation against alternatives. Hemolysis power-law constants taken from bovine blood literature without species correction. Model form uncertainty not quantified."
    },
