      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model inputs",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 5,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Probability distributions assigned to all influential input parameters (viscosity, density, inlet velocity profile) with Monte Carlo propagation to hemolysis QoI.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo study performed on flow rate and rotational speed only. Blood viscosity and inlet turbulence intensity treated as deterministic. Input uncertainty coverage incomplete for MRL 5."
    },
