      "acceptanceCriteria": "Formal equivalency mapping between simulation input parameters and experimental conditions documented with quantified tolerances.",
      "rationale": "No formal equivalency mapping produced. Fluid property differences between blood analog and patient blood not bridged. Epistemic gap flagged as unresolved at MRL 5."
